extendedInfo.description: This app features tips and information for college-bound high school students, organized alphabetically from A to Z. Use it as a helpful guide throughout the college application process. It will be a huge confidence booster. The information comes directly from an independent college admissions consultant with more than thirty-five years experience working with college-bound students and families. You know you are getting quality tips and resources. Free content updates will be delivered every so often and a link to the College Search Now website is provided.In addition to the tips themselves, the app provides links to helpful statistics, blogs, and other college preparation resources.Description of required permissions:Internet access: To open web pagesStorage: To read and write user preferences and other settings
